## Why this document exists

The project currently sits in private development with strong matrix-
honesty discipline (`<your audit-matrix invariant — e.g. "CODEC_BUG=0
across N field-cells">`; `<your verification harness>`; explicit
`<deliberate-deferral tier>`; honest capability declarations).  At
some point that discipline pays off only if the tool gets in front of
`<users / operators>` and starts catching the cells the internal
audit can't surface (the ones no fixture exercises).  This document
is the plan for crossing that boundary deliberately.

The plan is opinionated — it's not "here's an exhaustive menu" but
"here's the recommended path with rationale."  Adjust per-decision
when you start the wave.

