confused by Tier 1 will see "click here for the `<native installer>`."

### Tier 4 (optional): Native packages

| Package | Effort | Audience |
|---|---|---|
| Homebrew formula | Medium | macOS users |
| `.deb` / `.rpm` | Medium | Linux ops who avoid containers for policy reasons |
| Nix flake | Low (if you're into Nix) | Nix users; small but vocal |
| AUR | Low | Arch users |

Skip these for v0.1.0; add based on demand.  Tier 1 + 2 cover 95% of
installs.

